Package: supreme
Title: Structure Shiny application developed with modules
Description: supreme is a modeling tool helping you better structure 'Shiny' 
    applications developed with modules. You are able to: 1. Visualize relationship 
    of modules in existing applications 2. Design new applications from scratch
